### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### SYSTEM TEST — Auth + Presence + Log + Messaging
### Chạy trước khi test notification-service/file-service
### Click ▶ bên cạnh từng request theo thứ tự
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ═══ AUTH SERVICE (port 8081) ═══

### A1. Đăng ký user "nguyen"
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nguyen",
  "password": "123456"
}

### A2. Đăng nhập → lấy JWT token
# ⚠ COPY giá trị "token" từ response để dùng cho WebSocket!
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nguyen",
  "password": "123456"
}

### A3. Validate token (paste token vừa lấy)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJuZ3V5ZW4iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzgyMjcwNjcsImV4cCI6MTc3ODIzNDI2N30.dMyKe0GNuiuj0s1eby9IfoUGnJqNNVMctdQ0K6lhI_M"
}

### A4. Đăng ký user thứ 2 (để test chat)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "trang",
  "password": "123456"
}

### A5. Đăng nhập user thứ 2
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "trang",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ═══ PRESENCE SERVICE (port 8083) ═══

### P1. Đánh dấu nguyen online
POST http://localhost:8083/api/presence/connect?username=nguyen

### P2. Danh sách online
GET http://localhost:8083/api/presence/online

### P3. Kiểm tra trạng thái nguyen
GET http://localhost:8083/api/presence/status/nguyen

### P4. Đánh dấu nguyen offline
POST http://localhost:8083/api/presence/disconnect?username=nguyen

### ═══ LOG SERVICE (port 8084) ═══

### L1. Health check
GET http://localhost:8084/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### L2. Xem lịch sử log (ban đầu rỗng, có data sau khi chat qua WS)
GET http://localhost:8084/api/logs/history?page=0&size=50
Accept: application/json

### L3. Filter log theo eventType
GET http://localhost:8084/api/logs/history?page=0&size=50&eventType=CHAT
Accept: application/json

### ═══ MESSAGING (WebSocket — dùng wscat trong Terminal) ═══
#
# npm install -g wscat
#
# Terminal 1 (nguyen):
#   wscat -c "ws://localhost:8082/ws/chat?token=PASTE_TOKEN_NGUYEN"
#
# Terminal 2 (trang):
#   wscat -c "ws://localhost:8082/ws/chat?token=PASTE_TOKEN_TRANG"
#
# Gửi broadcast:
#   {"type":"CHAT","content":"Hello mọi người!"}
#
# Gửi private:
#   {"type":"PRIVATE","receiver":"trang","content":"Hi Trang riêng"}
#
# Sau khi chat xong → chạy L2 ở trên để xem log đã ghi chưa
